        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mt-3 text-[15px]" style="max-width:70ch;">Once treated as a Congo sub-type, the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Timneh_parrot" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-clay font-medium underline decoration-clay/30 hover:decoration-clay">Timneh is now recognized as a full species</a> with its own steadier temperament. For many families, every <a href="/timneh-african-grey-for-sale/" class="text-clay font-medium underline decoration-clay/30 hover:decoration-clay">Timneh African Grey we hand-raise</a> at C.A.Gs is the gentler, first-timer-friendly path into the world of Greys.</p>
